                            <comment id="60078" author="laisiyao" created="Thu, 6 Jun 2013 08:38:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Kit, could you tell me which file has the duplicate name in the testlog in your tarball? BTW, the reproducer program doesn&apos;t close file, which is strange. And is there a way to know when it should stop and quit? I haven&apos;t been able to reproduce yet.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
